昨天 13:54",,6a30e5330000000017028acd,note,6a30e5330000000017028acd,normal,滴滴出行不勾满所有车型就打不到车是吗？,我忍很久了，杀熟是吧？打了一个月的车，结果打车时间越来越长，派车距离越来越远，单价越来越贵，不把所有选项勾满，死活打不到车。不勾选就一直跳，否则打不到车。这么操作是怕你平台死得不够快吗？#滴滴打车[话题]# @滴滴出行客服,11,,False,none,False,,False,,1600,,,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606171018/d7d83a62dffb31421c3a378e462b4d9c/notes_pre_post/1040g3k0321fe55ng7u004a4lk801290iajcpve0!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,,1200,WB_PRV,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606171018/d7d83a62dffb31421c3a378e462b4d9c/notes_pre_post/1040g3k0321fe55ng7u004a4lk801290iajcpve0!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,WB_DFT,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606171018/5af6e3c150cfdc60e775bca860dbb1c3/notes_pre_post/1040g3k0321fe55ng7u004a4lk801290iajcpve0!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606171018/5af6e3c150cfdc60e775bca860dbb1c3/notes_pre_post/1040g3k0321fe55ng7u004a4lk801290iajcpve0!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,{},False,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,滴滴打车,topic,5c5181a8000000001c0319da,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,1781589299000,上海,https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/65ab3fad79eeb806753bb79e.jpg,ABrjRqUfgYa4k3RyhqMAT-IIs-xh3Tq7HtBhXHFYwCYJk=,5ad880114eacab2682342412,小福妈妈呀,61b2e3b8000000001000b65a,滴滴出行客服,ABVvFcK_3c6uLbstEyZA3gSywA2dSbby_YhqkqRfaM3aw=,1781589300000,False,1781662727605,"{""cursor_score"":"""",""items"":[{""id"":""6a30e5330000000017028acd"",""model_type"":""note"",""note_card"":{""tag_list"":[{""id"":""5c5181a8000000001c0319da"",""name"":""滴滴打车"",""type"":""topic""}],""time"":1781589299000,""last_update_time"":1781589300000,""note_id"":""6a30e5330000000017028acd"",""type"":""normal"",""desc"":""我忍很久了，杀熟是吧？打了一个月的车，结果打车时间越来越长，派车距离越来越远，单价越来越贵，不把所有选项勾满，死活打不到车。不勾选就一直跳，否则打不到车。这么操作是怕你平台死得不够快吗？#滴滴打车[话题]# @滴滴出行客服"",""interact_info"":{""relation"":""none"",""liked"":false,""liked_count"":"""",""collected"":false,""collected_count"":"""",""comment_count"":""11"",""share_count"":"""",""followed"":false},""ip_location"":""上海"",""share_info"":{""un_share"":false},""title"":""滴滴出行不勾满所有车