es_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng205qc0av0pgal216d25i0!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,{},,2796,,WB_PRV,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/d5d1d1083025c1f410a90f8bed08aaa8/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng2g5qc0av0pgal2src19i0!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/32c7834b15a8b555f12a625260231e31/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng2g5qc0av0pgal2src19i0!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,WB_DFT,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/d5d1d1083025c1f410a90f8bed08aaa8/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng2g5qc0av0pgal2src19i0!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,{},,2796,1290,,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/32c7834b15a8b555f12a625260231e31/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng2g5qc0av0pgal2src19i0!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,False,,1290,,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/05ee2780dd60466740bcd77448c07c45/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng305qc0av0pgal24u1q5gg!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,WB_PRV,WB_DFT,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/9269bf122e44996006e202ea7f5080c8/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng305qc0av0pgal24u1q5gg!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/05ee2780dd60466740bcd77448c07c45/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng305qc0av0pgal24u1q5gg!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/9269bf122e44996006e202ea7f5080c8/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng305qc0av0pgal24u1q5gg!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,False,,2796,,{},1290,,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/0a853e396fa6057169412f62e6bf647a/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng3g5qc0av0pgal25avik7o!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,False,,2796,,WB_PRV,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/9ab093201c55eef52f7df0e650d51b28/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng3g5qc0av0pgal25avik7o!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,WB_DFT,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/0a853e396fa6057169412f62e6bf647a/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng3g5qc0av0pgal25avik7o!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/9ab093201c55eef52f7df0e650d51b28/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng3g5qc0av0pgal25avik7o!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,{},滴滴出行,topic,5c98635a000000000d03fb1d,谁来管一管,topic,61ab320e0000000001007f61,topic,5c7cf36a000000000f00ac4a,消费者权益,5fb4c0fe0000000001007f7a,误导消费者,topic,,,,,,,,,,,,,1781664369000,新加坡,https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/645b65431e7abf18da7d1266.jpg,ABVOUe8wqFL89-TplzkBNi6r5r77Wr_pXU2d5eC5U4nmM=,698057c10000000026002aa2,iSaskue,5b00200ee8ac2b4e8b97b408,滴滴美好出发,ABA8u8mNMoi6f73YeiZDoY1EsE9VXLoQHDPjIrs9yL1Ws=,1781664369000,False,1781749491665,"{""cursor_score"":"""",""items"":[{""id"":""6a320a71000000000e038400"",""model_type"":""note"",""note_card"":{""type"":""normal"",""desc"":""事情是这样的：\n6.5凌晨落地西安使用滴滴打车，勾选了超值出租车+特惠快车，预估价格100左右，超值出租车接单\n到达后滴滴显示车费136.8+过路费6，过路费没问题，但超值出租车是一口价，和结算价差这么多，然后我就问滴滴客服原因，简要的问答如下：\n\t\n【第一段对话】\n我：超值出租车是一口价吗？\n滴滴：是的\n我：那为啥我这个结算价和一口价差这么多？\n滴滴：您上车有指定路线之类的吗？\n我：没有的，就是按照推荐的导航路线走的\n滴滴：稍等我查看一下\n滴滴：您勾选了特惠快车和超值出租车，系统又推荐了出租车等车型，所以价格是按照打表计价的\n我：我是没有勾选的，而且我打到的车就是超值出租车\n滴滴：需要授权车内录音，48小时内会有专员跟您联系\n\t\n【第二段对话】\n滴滴：针对您反馈的司机加价的问题，我们已经对司机会进行培训、并密切关注\n我：我不是想问司机加价的问题，我是想问我消费前显示一口价，为什么消费后你们系统是另一个价格\n滴滴：您认可6元的高速过路费吗？\n我：我的问题一直不是这6元的过路费，而是消费前系统显示一口价、消费后系统显示打表价，为什么计价规格会变\n滴滴：我们只是提供打车撮合服务，我们不提供运输服务\n我：我问的就是你们系统处理机制，为什么一口价会变成打表价\n滴滴：我们核实后48小时内回电，订单已锁定\n然后我想着司机师傅大半夜接单也不容易，想着支付了再说，结果支付时发现订单已锁定、无法支付。\n但是第二天滴滴系统给我自动扣款（因为我之前设置过免密支付，但是这种存在争议的金额、并且滴滴已经锁定订单了，还能通过免密支付划走我的钱）\n\t\n隔天默默的来了个短信（见最后一个截图）\n\t\n【第三段对话-语音客服】\n我：我反馈的问题为什么没有人联系我呢？\n滴滴：您反馈的是司机在车费中加了6元过路费的问题吗？\n我：我反馈的是什么问题你们都不知道？然后让我等了48小时又48小时的？\n滴滴：您说一下需要反馈的问题，我记录一下，48小时内给您反馈\n我：（又把我的诉求说了一遍）\n\t\n然后截至发稿、还没有滴滴客服联系我[doge][doge]，估计人家钱已经到口袋了，也就懒得管了，毕竟整个行业滴滴一家独大，压榨司机这块儿就不说了，对消费者也是搪塞了事，转个人工都得喊好几次转人工才行，唉…人家想干啥就干啥吧\n\t\n#滴滴出行[话题]# #谁来管一管[话题]# #消费者权益[话题]##误导消费者[话题]#\n@滴滴美好出发 @滴滴"",""share_info"":{""un_share"":false},""illegal_info"":{""left_icon"":""https://picasso-static.xiaohongshu.com/fe-platfrom/bc740cc162107169b504c4c1e5ee35f92eaa8456.png""},""title"":""滴滴一家独大🤫🤫"",""interact_info"":{""comment_count"":""6"",""share_count"":""1"",""followed"":false,""relation"":""none"",""liked"":false,""liked_count"":""1"",""collected"":false,""collected_count"":""""},""image_list"":[{""info_list"":[{""image_scene"":""WB_PRV"",""url"":""http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/d6c5bc2ebd277873fecc625c5b51ee2e/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng105qc0av0pgal28aop46g!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3""},{""image_scene"":""WB_DFT"",""url"":""http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/dba061e797291bf3dc0f69309d3a4203/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng105qc0av0pgal28aop46g!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3""}],""url_pre"":""http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/d6c5bc2ebd277873fecc625c5b51ee2e/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng105qc0av0pgal28aop46g!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3"",""url_default"":""http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/dba061e797291bf3dc0f69309d3a4203/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng105qc0av0pgal28aop46g!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3"",""stream"":{},""height"":2796,""width"":1290,""trace_id"":"""",""file_id"":"""",""url"":"""",""live_photo"":false},{""url_pre"":""http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/1c6f020ae4b9142ce8618bc9e884c0c5/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng1g5qc0av0pgal2ntise98!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3"",""url_default"":""http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/d5f68ae57fa1b1be49b28e3a4fd7b9a4/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng1g5qc0av0pgal2ntise98!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3"",""live_photo"":false,""file_id"":"""",""width"":1290,""url"":"""",""trace_id"":"""",""info_list"":[{""image_scene"":""WB_PRV"",""url"":""http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/1c6f020ae4b9142ce8618bc9e884c0c5/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng1g5qc0av0pgal2ntise98!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3""},{""image_scene"":""WB_DFT"",""url"":""http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606181024/d5f68ae57fa1b1be49b28e3a4fd7b9a4/oss-sg/notes_pre_post/1040g3mo321ggnnr8ng1g5qc0av0pgal2ntise98!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3""}],""height"":2796,""stream"":{}},{""file_id"":"""",""height"":2796,""url_default"":""h