滴滴轻享,https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result_ai?keyword=%E6%BB%B4%E6%BB%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%AB&source=web_explore_feed,97,https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result/6a37a7eb0000000021023ddb?xsec_token=ABKcpdiNookDSeXJp_XLZsdRdZoqH8m_9TJuSszFUN77I=&xsec_source=,6a37a7eb0000000021023ddb,,滴滴代驾，随意扔客人路边，连车门都不给我关,"芳哥哥
昨天 16:59",,6a37a7eb0000000021023ddb,note,6a37a7eb0000000021023ddb,normal,滴滴代驾，随意扔客人路边，连车门都不给我关,"酒后找了代驾，前后说了四遍开慢点。最后给我扔路边了。
第一次，出了小区就五十迈，跟代驾师傅说慢一点，告诉我开的不快。
第二次，被猛踩猛杀不太舒服，再次说慢一点，告诉我没到限速（我是电车，在二排坐着，被晃来晃去）。
第三次，再次提及慢一点，太快不舒服，告诉我慢下来没发开，让我把窗户关上就好了。
第四次，再次开口说喝了酒了开慢点。代驾再次怼了我，告诉我开的不快，张口怨我谁让你喝了酒了。随后我们让他停到了路边，告诉我没法开暗示我们在找一个，后续就是他走了，车门开着，后备箱开着，给停在了大马路边。
当晚我就在联系客服，搞笑的是，客服的服务时间是9-24。没办法只能重新下单。今天滴滴给我回电客服告诉我。他们只是一个平台。没有办法要求更多。滴滴。你真的是好起来就忘本。我不理解，找个代驾比祖宗还难伺候@滴滴代驾 你们的代驾都是这么厉害的吗。#代驾[话题]#",25,,False,none,False,,False,,2796,,,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220853/c3661ddb02dd39b53279dd65b77e17a6/notes_pre_post/1040g3k8321m104k7na705n1ujemhrt6lgqkujr0!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,,1290,WB_PRV,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220853/c3661ddb02dd39b53279dd65b77e17a6/notes_pre_post/1040g3k8321m104k7na705n1ujemhrt6lgqkujr0!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,WB_DFT,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220853/7e9d6cc4b26b30e4b2605ebf5db995bb/notes_pre_post/1040g3k8321m104k7na705n1ujemhrt6lgqkujr0!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220853/7e9d6cc4b26b30e4b2605ebf5db995bb/notes_pre_post/1040g3k8321m104k7na705n1ujemhrt6lgqkujr0!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,{},False,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,代驾,topic,5c65cad3000000000f036d54,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,1782032364000,河北,https://sns-avatar-qc.xhscdn.com/avatar/529594cd91bbf4c43608131bf9134bdc.jpg,ABAwBJ4padHLzu3DHvuSSyPxWNJ-Wbpo_WdbO9aTSxp1U=,5c3e9bad000000000701f4d5,芳哥哥,63478cf4000000001901f54e,滴滴代驾,ABDN6bmVuKBNABDAajolUnF17VXQcq69N5iFgI-lwu76Q=,1782032364000,False,1782089612263,"{""cursor_score"":"""",""items"":[{""note_card"":{""ip_location"":""河北"",""type"":""normal"",""title"":""滴滴代驾，随意扔客人路边，连车门都不给我关"",""interact_info"":{""liked"":false,""liked_count"":"""",""collected"":false,""collected_count"":"""",""comment_count"":""25"",""share_count"":"""",""followed"":false,""relation"":""none""},""image_list"":[{""url"":"""",""info_list"":[{""url"":""http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220853/c3661ddb02dd39b53279dd65b77e17a6/notes_pre_post/1040g3k8321m104k7na705n1ujemhrt6lgqkujr0!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3"",""image_scene"":""WB_PRV""},{""image_scene"":""WB_DFT"",""url"":""http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220853/7e9d6cc4b26b30e4b2605ebf5db995bb/notes_pre_post/1040g3k8321m104k7na705n1ujemhrt6lgqkujr0!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3""}],""url_pre"":""http://sns-webpic-q