1天前",,6a372eb3000000000f028de8,note,6a372eb3000000000f028de8,normal,勇闯猿辅导day4,马上培训期就要结束了，第四天主要是看视频纠正一下发音以及一些介绍，然后晚上继续学习打电话[叹气R] ，因为晚上下雨就等到了十点半去楼下用企业版滴滴打车（这个还挺好用的，就是人多的时候要等挺久才能打到车），总体来说还可以，我们一起培训的这些人里好像也就两三个走了的，而且我觉得第二、三天能撑过的应该就是可以接受这个工作#新人入职[话题]# #实习日记[话题]# #实习[话题]# #我的找工作日记[话题]# #入职[话题]# #上班第一天[话题]# #大学生实习[话题]# #实习生日常[话题]#,5,,False,none,False,7,False,,4096,,,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220904/be09fc418381d5b66fecc2cd23b09c5e/1040g008321lia12in45g5nkl6bvg8lgpmiko5n8!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,,3072,WB_PRV,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220904/be09fc418381d5b66fecc2cd23b09c5e/1040g008321lia12in45g5nkl6bvg8lgpmiko5n8!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,WB_DFT,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220904/672d351c6a610ad53d0f8091dfbb3111/1040g008321lia12in45g5nkl6bvg8lgpmiko5n8!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220904/672d351c6a610ad53d0f8091dfbb3111/1040g008321lia12in45g5nkl6bvg8lgpmiko5n8!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,{},False,WB_PRV,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220904/56996e383a11c0de56362025442da577/1040g008321lia12in4505nkl6bvg8lgp2alhino!nd_prv_wgth_webp_3,WB_DFT,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220904/d0abdf28672d3d8a4c65e21a6f882c4d/1040g008321lia12in4505nkl6bvg8lgp2alhino!nd_dft_wgth_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220904/56996e383a11c0de56362025442da577/1040g008321lia12in4505nkl6bvg8lgp2alhino!nd_prv_wgth_webp_3,,,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220904/d0abdf28672d3d8a4c65e21a6f882c4d/1040g008321lia12in4505nkl6bvg8lgp2alhino!nd_dft_wgth_webp_3,{},False,,3072,4096,False,1200,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220904/00c336f49637f6ea300adce384402b60/1040g008321lia12in40g5nkl6bvg8lgpevct1do!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220904/0b43b42f925da5d0c40f050713b1bd22/1040g008321lia12in40g5nkl6bvg8lgpevct1do!nd_dft_wlteh_webp_3,,WB_PRV,http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202606220904/00c336f49637f6ea300adce384402b60/1040g008321lia12in40g5nkl6bvg8lgpevct1do!nd_prv_wlteh_webp_3,WB_DFT,http://sns-webpic-qc.x